social_posts.post_text: The mountains are the one place in California that feels like we’re back home in the snow🤍
Home for the holidays🎄 #ad
Wrapping up the year with some holiday cheer🎁 #ad
A dream come true🤍💍 @christian
My very first bachelor’s apartment project🖤 I’m calling it “masculine chic”

I toured this apartment with my friend before he moved in and couldn’t stop thinking about how cute it could be with just some furniture & decor! No need to paint, remove flooring, or make any major changes sometimes! All you need is some stylish pieces & decor styling to make an empty apartment to pull it all together and make it feel like home🤍🏡 - full makeover is over on my channel!

The coziest family room there ever was🤍 

Believe it or not, at some point in time this room was considered the 4th bedroom in our house. It’s right off the entryway, the first space you can peak into and I always pictured it being a bold & beautiful family room! After not putting any time into it for 2 years, I finally tackled the project with the plan of completely changing the look of it! Dark, moody, bold & cozy was the plan! It’s taken me about a month to transform this room but I finally turned it into the family room I always imagined! It was the perfect size space to paint a dark color (BM: Intrigue), transform the closet into a bar, add detail molding & style the room with collected thrifted decor to make this space feel like its been here forever! I love it, we love it & it’s our new favorite room in the house!☺️
My new morning corner🤍✨ this little corner gets flooded with light in the morning making it the perfect spot for coffee and morning snuggles with Henry!
Family room glow up✨

There’s nothing like waking up to sun shining through the windows & a private cozy space to retreat to at night! The best thing I’ve ever installed in our home are my favorite Serena Smart Shades by @lutronelectronics ✨  #lutronambassador  #smarterwithserena #sponsored
Getting our small garden patio ready for Spring☀️🌷
Just a couple happy campers🏕️
Our lake house patio is finally complete! Just in time to enjoy all Summer patio season long☀️🌸🍹 Watch the entire transformation over on my channel now!
Enjoying the ambiance on the patio in the evening is easier with our @lutronelectronics Caséta Outdoor Smart Plug!✨ #lutronambassador #CasetaSmarterLighting #sponsored

In my bridal era👰🏼‍♀️🤍

I started the wedding dress shopping journey in Toronto and now I’m continuing the search in LA! I’ve tried on mermaids, A-lines, ball gowns, capes, fit and flares, strapless, gloves, sleeves and now I think I’m finally narrowing down what I’m looking for! I know I need to find a dress but I also don’t want this experience to end! It’s too much fun!!
What an incredible week in San Diego at the 2nd annual Amazon Creators Summit 🤍 Feeling so honored, grateful, and inspired✨ #amazoncreatorsummit

When you want to feel inspired, it matters where you stay!✨ I’m all about getting the full experience during my travels by immersing myself in unique design and architecture, trying new foods & beverages, all without leaving the hotel! I’m always looking for one-of-a-kind experiences and the historic beachfront resort The Hotel Del Coronado @curiocollection by @hilton was everything I could have dreamed of and more! @delcoronado #hiltonpartner
This is where we end up when I google “fun things to do near me” 🎃🥧🍂

When the viral Christmas tree is sold out everywhere… the next best thing is a rotating Christmas tree stand🎄✨ it’s instant magic! I’m officially in the holiday spirit after putting up my first of two Christmas trees in our home! 

#viralchristmastree #rotatingchristmastreestand #christmasdecor #christmastree

These shorter Winter days just mean I get more cozy time at home!🎄✨ The warm glow of lamps fill our home every evening by turning on automatically using Caséta by @lutronelectronics Lamp Dimming Smar Plugs and it’s my favorite thing ever! #lutronamassador #casetasmarterlighting #sponsored #casetawireless #smartlighting

This year changed my life🤍 I got engaged to the love of my life, started planning our wedding 2024 wedding, tried new things in my career I’ve always shied away from, dipped our toes into the home buying process and started seriously thinking about where we want to grow our roots. 2024 is going to be a big year of change and I’m so excited for it!
